==Early==
*Having learned from [[Aranarth]] about [[Kings of Arthedain|King]] [[Arvedui]], [[Cirdan]] sends an elven ship to [[Forochel]] to rescue him.<ref name=eriador>{{App|Eriador}}</ref>

==March==
*Long winter, the ice of the north remains longer than usual.<ref name=eriador/>
* [[Arvedui]] drowned in the [[Icebay of Forochel]].<ref name=eriador/><ref name="TA">{{App|TA}}</ref>
* The ''[[palantíri]]'' of [[Annúminas]] and [[Weathertop|Amon Sûl]] are lost.<ref name=eriador/><ref name="TA"/> The [[Ring of Barahir]] stays with the chief of the [[Lossoth]].<ref name=eriador/>

==Later==
* [[Angmar conflict]]: [[Eärnur]] brings a fleet to [[Lindon]].<ref name="TA"/><ref name=gondor>{{App|Gondor}}</ref>
* The [[Host of the West (Arnor)|Host of the West]] is assembled; [[Glorfindel]]  with a force from [[Rivendell]] joins them.<ref name=gondor/>
*The [[Witch-king]] defeated at the [[Battle of Fornost]]. He is pursued to the [[Ettenmoors]] where Eärnur fails to fight him. He vanishes from the North.<ref name="TA"/><ref name=gondor/>
